  "artist": {
    "bio": "Benjamin Franklin, Parisian DJ and producer, has been a key figure in the house scene for over 20 years. Trained in the legendary clubs of the 90s — Les Bains Douches, La Locomotive, Le Queen — he forged a unique sound blending house, soul and Latin rhythms. His legendary 'Who The Fuck Is Benjamin Franklin?' parties have set dancefloors on fire from Paris to Miami, through Buenos Aires. Signed to MIYU Records, his productions like 'This Is My House', 'Chupa Sin Mano' and 'THIS SOUND' are played by the biggest DJs around the world, from Ultra Music Festival to Tomorrowland. In 2025, he returns with a new wave of productions blending deep percussive beats and Latin energy, confirming his status as a reference in international house music."
  },
